§ DIAGNOSTIC-RECIPE
  1. Build minimal-exe with explicit-eprintln + explicit-flush
  2. Attach-debugger (Visual-Studio) to-check call-site
  3. Compare-IR before/after recent body_lower-changes via csslc-debug-output
  4. Test on-non-Windows-target if-possible

§ WNDPROC @ 144HZ
  PeekMessage + DispatchMessage in-tight-loop with-high-resolution-timer
  OR WaitForSingleObject on-swapchain-fence
  GetMessage BLOCKS → starves 144hz · DON'T-USE
  Trade-off : PeekMessage burns-CPU · mitigate with 1ms-sleep OR Present-timing

§ MIN-VIABLE D3D12 SWAPCHAIN
  Steps :
    1. Create ID3D12Device + ID3D12CommandQueue
    2. IDXGISwapChain1 via CreateSwapChainForHwnd
       2 buffers · Rgba16FloatHdr10 · DXGI_SWAP_CHAIN_FLAG_ALLOW_TEARING
    3. Create RTV-heap + views
    4. Clear + present in-loop
    5. SKIP : PSO · root-sig · shaders
  Estimate : ~200 LOC to-first-frame

